metadata.description: Commemorative Infanity Founding Fans Jewl. Become a talent scout and brand ambassador for Infanity, a music platform for independent artists, founded by music industry veterans.* You will also receive priority access to Infanity events and early access to new products and services. In addition, you will have the opportunity to participate in exclusive community events and initiatives. This is a limited 500 piece collection.
